        <updateDate>2019-12-03T14:52:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Lifetime Learning Credit Enhancement Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the lifetime learning tax credit, to increase the taxpayer income ceiling for purposes of the phaseout of such credit. Under current law, the phaseout of the credit begins for a taxpayer with a modified adjusted gross income over $40,000 ($80,000 for joint returns). This bill doubles those amounts.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
